{
  "texts": [
    "Bubeck et al. [230] conducted various human-crafted tests on GPT-4.",
    "It can be observed that GPT-4 performs close to or even exceeds human performance on various tasks.",
    "In practice, automated evaluation and human evaluation are considered for adoption on a case-by-case basis.Training Data-based FM Evaluation: During fine-tuning, the training data might not be equally important for a pre-trained FM.",
    "On the one hand, pre-trained FMs are prone to significant performance degradation with noisy data.",
    "This effect can be further amplified when noisy samples are highly influential to the model."
  ]
}